n any build-up that may be present, do not unscrew the aerator. if the problem persists, please submit amaintenance request.please remember that it is the responsibility of the residents to clean up any excess hair or clutter in the sink areamaintenance can repair a problem.mon - fri8:00am-5:00pm pst